name: Zack3D-Kinky
description:
Zack3D kinky is a model aimed at the more kinkier side of furry art. Goo, transformation, tentacles, that sort of stuff. Trained off of base 1.5, this model has been around for a while. Only recently have I started focusing it down into a goal: Realistic furries along with more advanced kinks. With this original unfocused v1 model, this v2 model is able to do non-kinky as well, and some topics that surprise even me!

If you have any questions about the model, feel free to join my Furry Goo/Latex discord server
If you have more questions about who I am, my Linktree

modelVersions.name: Zack3D-Kinky-v2
modelVersions.description:
First public release of v2, refocusing on the kinkier side and trying to be more ethical with the handling of images.

This release was trained with bucketing on top of v1, with 20k images instead of 200k. It can do non-square ratios but it can be a bit more finicky to prompt.
